[Liu Hongyi, Polisi Kabupaten Yicheng]

512
00:27:48,240 --> 00:27:48,700
Barang tersebut...

513
00:27:49,160 --> 00:27:50,010
Apakah kamu menerimanya?

514
00:27:50,270 --> 00:27:50,660
Jangan khawatir.

515
