539
00:32:38,550 --> 00:32:39,090
Ku...

540
00:32:39,590 --> 00:32:43,860
Nama saya bukan Changhong Jade.

541
00:32:46,240 --> 00:32:47,330
Anda bisa berbicara secara orisinal.

542
00:32:51,160 --> 00:32:54,810
Sejak aku minum

543
